		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare (Requires Nonthing)</em></p><p><em>Warrior spirits from the plane of Ysgard appear</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Action</strong> - 60 ft. - 1 Hour - 1/7 Days</p></li><li><p>You summon 2 undead @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-summoned-creatures.Actor.DeCBNvD7CVmHPljj]{bersekers}.</p></li><li><p>The spirits look like living, breathing warriors, and they have Immunity to the &amp;Reference[Charmed apply=false] and &amp;Reference[Frightened apply=false] conditions.</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Attack</strong></p><ul><li><p>If you blow the horn without meeting its requirement, the summoned spirits attack you. If you meet the requirement, they are Friendly to you and your allies and follow your commands.</p></li></ul>",
